These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-1::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, cycling
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, cauliflower
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Sport   | soccer  | cycling |
| Food     | cauliflower | cabbage  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: turquise, coral
2 different games are played: go, backgammon
1. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |      2       |
| Color    | turquise      | coral         |
| Game   | go | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-3::.
House: colonial, cape-cod
There are 2 different nationalities: malaysian, russian
1. the colonial house is on the right of the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |
| House   | cape-cod | colonial   |
| Nationality       | russian  | malaysian |

 #################################

 
