.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-1-7::.
City: hamburg, london
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, balloon-flower
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |
| City   | hamburg | london |
